He may not be a member of the academy of sciences but there is a
well known coding theorist/mathematician by that name. He has developed
a tight lower bound on mutual correlations of sets of sequences 
over the complex numbers. He may or may not be the same V.M. Sidelnikov
referred to in the previous articles.

